g 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/slipknot-clown@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">Slipknot</a>的 Shawn &#39;Clown&#39; Crahan 谈到了乐队“丢失的专辑”“Look Outside Your Window”的推迟。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-tour-2024-tickets-new-material-3559353">活结乐队的小丑谈论 2024 年巡演和新材料：“这支乐队从未如此快乐”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该歌曲由主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corey-taylor">Corey Taylor</a> 、Sid Wilson、Jim Root 和 Shawn &#39;Clown&#39; Crahan 录制，当时乐队正在制作 2008 年的歌曲“All Hope Is Gone”。有一次，泰勒试图将两张唱片合二为一，但“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-slipknot-all-hope-is-hope-gone-outtakes-experimental-radiohead-2541951">超级实验性的、充满活力的</a>”曲目并没有融合在一起。迄今为止，仅发布了一首曲目——“All Hope Is Gone”的附赠曲目“Til We Die”。</p><p>这张专辑长期以来一直受到参与成员的调侃，主唱科里·泰勒(Corey Taylor)去年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-teases-release-of-slipknots-lost-album-look-outside-your-window-3482056">调侃这张专辑的发行</a>，再次火上浇油。此后专辑的进展有所加快，《小丑》现在提供了这张期待已久的唱片的最新消息。 </p><figure id="attachment_3600001" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3600001" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3600001" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3600001" class="wp-caption-text">活结乐团的科里·泰勒。图片来源：Venla Shalin/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>这位打击乐手兼乐队领军人物在接受<a href="https://www.vulture.com/article/slipknot-clown-shawn-crahan-best-songs.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Vulture</em></a>采访时谈到 Slipknot 未发行的作品时说道：“我什至不知道从哪里开始。我的意思是，有音频，然后还有视频。我们有大量不完整的概念，有些刚刚完成。我希望文化中能够有很多活结。在我的整个职业生涯中，我创造了很多东西，但真正付诸实践的却非常非常少。”</p><p>然后他谈到了《看看窗外》，并补充道：“没有人相信它存在，或者它会出现。我一直高度评价它，我总是说你永远不会听到科里·泰勒这样唱歌。在我看来，这只是一种完全不同的方法。最近，我批准了所有的艺术作品。我也非常努力地混合和掌握它。”</p><p>该乐队今年还忙着举行 25 周年巡演，并宣布了 2025 年在多个地区进行巡演。他们最近分享了 2025 年欧洲巡演的日期，该巡演定于明年夏天开始。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-announce-2025-european-tour-3809436">您可以在此处找到完整的日期列表和票务信息</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3774132" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3774132" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3774132" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min.jpg" alt="活结乐队的 Shawn “Clown” Crahan 摄影：Chelsea Guglielmino" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3774132" class="wp-caption-text">活结乐队的 Shawn “Clown” Crahan 摄影：Chelsea Guglielmino</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-tour-2024-tickets-new-material-3559353">去年 12 月，克拉汉在接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>表示，《看看窗外》“肯定”将于 2024 年发行：“我向你保证。艺术已经完成了。已经混在一起了已经掌握了。它肯定会在 2024 年发行，这是一张非常棒的专辑。”</p><p>泰勒去年在接受<em>NME</em>采访时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lost-slipknot-album-look-outside-your-window-could-be-released-this-year-says-clown-3373724">给出了进一步的更新，并表示这张唱片尚未发行部分是他的错</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" id="33330167" title="Corey Taylor 谈论“CMF2”、PTSD 意识以及 Slipknot 的下一步发展" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jhKn5spvKbQ?feature=oembed&amp;enablejsapi=1" width="100%" height="392" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" data-gtm-yt-inspected-6="true" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe></p><p>当被问及这张唱片时，他回答说：“你提到这个实际上很有趣。有一天我和小丑谈论这件事，他说，“它没有问世的原因之一是因为你一直在发布垃圾，这与我想发布它的时间一直相冲突！”我当时想，‘操老兄，你为什么不告诉我？’他说，“操，泰勒——你真是太狗屎了！”听起来他终于可以锁定发布日期了，我已经向他保证我不会发布任何会破坏这一日期的内容。我想这将是明年——终于，伙计！” </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-announce-2025-european-tour-3809436"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>在其他新闻中，活结乐队的粉丝最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-fans-react-to-new-s-logo-on-new-merch-absolutely-not-3808093">对他们的新商品上出现的乐队新“S”标志做出了反应</a>，许多人对这个设计不太满意。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknots-clown-explains-delay-of-lost-album-look-outside-your-window-3809946">活结小丑解释“丢失专辑”《Look Outside Your Window》的延迟的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
迈克尔·杰克逊传记片推迟至 2025 年底上映https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-jackson-biopic-delayed-to-late-2025-3809939?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=michael-jackson-biopic-delayed-to-late-2025Surej Singh Wed, 06 Nov 2024 04:10:16 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3809939 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>原定于明年四月首播</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-jackson-biopic-delayed-to-late-2025-3809939">迈克尔·杰克逊传记片推迟到 2025 年末</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首发。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>即将上映的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-jackson">迈克尔·杰克逊</a>传记片已推迟至 2025 年——了解更多信息如下。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="650" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/quincy-jones-obituary-3809386"><b>昆西·琼斯，1933-2024：眼中闪烁着光芒打破界限的超级制片人</b></a></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-jackson-biopic-in-the-works-by-bohemian-rhapsody-producer-3156367"><em>《迈克尔》</em></a>是 Antoine Fuqua 为狮门影业制作的下一个项目，原定于 2025 年 4 月在美国上映。现在， <a href="https://deadline.com/2024/11/michael-jackson-biopic-good-fortune-release-date-1236167786/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Deadline</em></a>证实狮门影业已经推迟了这部备受期待的传记片的上映，以便将这部电影定位在“颁奖走廊”。</p><p>该片目前定于 10 月 3 日在美国上映，全球首映日期尚未公布。 <em>《迈克尔》</em>将由环球影业在全球发行。</p><p>截至目前，有关这部电影的公开信息有限。它的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/michael-jackson-biopic-trailer-goes-down-well-with-critics-at-cinemacon-3616660">第一部预告片于四月份在 CinemaCon 上向评论家透露，据报道受到好评</a>，但尚未向公众发布。 </p><figure id="attachment_3785983" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3785983" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3785983" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing.jpg" alt="1996 年 7 月 16 日，迈克尔·杰克逊在文莱向估计 60,000 名观众表演。（照片来源应为 FRANCIS Sylvain/AFP via Getty Images）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3785983" class="wp-caption-text"> 1996 年 7 月 16 日，迈克尔·杰克逊在文莱向估计 60,000 名观众表演。（照片来源应为 FRANCIS Sylvain/AFP via Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>制片人格雷厄姆·金今年四月证实，该项目正处于制作中途。 “我们对这部电影感到无比自豪。我期待着为观众呈现一部他们从未见过的电影，”金说。</p><p>他还分享道：“当你提到他的名字时，每个人都有自己的看法。这是第一次……一代又一代的电影观众将齐聚一堂，深入了解这位有史以来最多产的艺术家。”</p><p>这部电影将讲述迈克尔·杰克逊的生活和职业生涯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-jackson-to-be-played-by-his-nephew-jaafar-in-upcoming-biopic-3389628">，由迈克尔·杰克逊的侄子贾法尔·杰克逊</a>主演。电影中的其他演员包括饰演乔·杰克逊的科尔曼·多明戈和饰演经理约翰·布兰卡的迈尔斯·特勒。</p><p> <em>《吸血鬼日记》</em>明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-vampire-diaries-star-to-portray-diana-ross-in-michael-jackson-biopic-3609373">凯特·格雷厄姆将饰演标志性的戴安娜·罗斯</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-producer-and-songwriter-quincy-jones-has-died-aged-91-3809203">本周早些时候去世的</a>行业巨头<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/quincy-jones">昆西·琼斯</a>将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/insecure"><em>《不安全</em></a>》的肯德里克·桑普森饰演。</p><p>到目前为止，电影中只发布了一张图片，贾法尔·杰克逊穿着迈克尔最具标志性的造型。您可以看到下图。 </p><figure id="attachment_3599127" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3599127" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3599127" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024-1392x2088.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024-1068x1602.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3599127" class="wp-caption-text">贾法尔·杰克逊在《迈克尔》中饰演迈克尔·杰克逊。照片来源：凯文·马祖尔</figcaption></figure><p>就在电影推迟上映的消息传出后几天，迈克尔·杰克逊标志性专辑“Thriller”的联合制作人昆西·琼斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-producer-and-songwriter-quincy-jones-has-died-aged-91-3809203">去世，享年 91 岁</a>。</p><p>琼斯去世后，包括保罗·麦卡特尼、 <a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/stevie-wonder-quincy-jones-tribute-2-1235153268/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">史蒂夫·旺德</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dion-honours-musical-genius-and-cherished-mentor-quincy-jones-after-his-death-3809928">席琳·迪翁</a>在内的众多音乐巨星纷纷<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/quincy-jones-obituary-3809386">向这位传奇制作人致敬</a>。</p><p>在其他音乐电影新闻中，最近有消息称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknds-upcoming-film-with-jenna-ortega-and-barry-keoghan-to-tie-into-hurry-up-tomorrow-album-3809535">The Weeknd 即将与珍娜·奥尔特加 (Jenna Ortega) 和巴里·基奥根 (Barry Keoghan) 合作的电影将与这位加拿大音乐家即将发行的唱片《明天快点》(Hurry Up Tomorrow) 结合在一起</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-jackson-biopic-delayed-to-late-2025-3809939">迈克尔·杰克逊传记片推迟到 2025 年末</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首发。</p> ;
